author: arkurth
msg: Updated Module.pm to not attempt to call initialize if running in setup mode. In this mode, vcld attempts to create an object for each module. However, a valid reservation DataStructure object does not exist which can be passed to the module. This causes problems if a module has an initialize subroutine which expects a valid DataStructure object.
